    DRPID,

)

    :DRRT,
    :DRKY,

    :DRUDCO,
    :DRHRDC,
    :DRUSER,
    :DRPID,
    :DRUPMJ,
    :DRJOBN,
    :DRUPMT
)

    F0005
WHERE
    DRSY = :DRSY

SET

    DRDL02 = :DRDL02,

MERGE INTO #SCHEMA.SY#.F00926 t
USING (
  SELECT 
    :AUUSER AS AUUSER,
    :AUWUID AS AUWUID,
    :AUROLEDESC AS AUROLEDESC,
    :AULNGP AS AULNGP,
    :AUSEQNO AS AUSEQNO,
    :AUEMLA AS AUEMLA ,
    :AULASTLOGIN AS AULASTLOGIN,
    :AUUSEINTENSE AS AUUSEINTENSE,
    :AUWEBIDCRE AS AUWEBIDCRE,
    :AUACTINACT AS AUACTINACT,
    :AUFUTANON1 AS AUFUTANON1,
    :AUFUTANON2 AS AUFUTANON2,
    :AUFUTANON10 AS AUFUTANON10,
    :AUFUTANON11 AS AUFUTANON11,

    :AUFUTANON13 AS AUFUTANON13,
    :AUFUTANON14 AS AUFUTANON14,
    :AUFUTANON15 AS AUFUTANON15,
    :AUFUTANON16 AS AUFUTANON16,
    :AUMUSE AS AUMUSE,
    :AUPID AS AUPID,
    :AUJOBN AS AUJOBN,
    :AUUPMJ AS AUUPMJ,
    :AUUPMT AS AUUPMT 
  FROM dual) src
ON (t.AUUSER = src.AUUSER )
WHEN MATCHED THEN
  UPDATE SET 
    t.AUWUID = src.AUWUID,
    t.AUROLEDESC = src.AUROLEDESC,
    t.AUSEQNO = src.AUSEQNO,
    t.AUEMLA = src.AUEMLA,
    t.AULASTLOGIN = src.AULASTLOGIN,
    t.AUUSEINTENSE = src.AUUSEINTENSE,
    t.AUWEBIDCRE = src.AUWEBIDCRE,
    t.AUACTINACT = src.AUACTINACT,
    t.AUFUTANON1 = src.AUFUTANON1,
    t.AUFUTANON2 = src.AUFUTANON2,
    t.AUFUTANON10 = src.AUFUTANON10,
    t.AUFUTANON11 = src.AUFUTANON11,
    t.AUFUTANON12 = src.AUFUTANON12,
    t.AUFUTANON3 = src.AUFUTANON3,
    t.AUFUTANON4 = src.AUFUTANON4,
    t.AUFUTANON5 = src.AUFUTANON5,
    t.AUFUTANON6 = src.AUFUTANON6,
    t.AUFUTANON7 = src.AUFUTANON7,
    t.AUFUTANON8 = src.AUFUTANON8,
    t.AUFUTANON9 = src.AUFUTANON9,
    t.AUFUTANON13 = src.AUFUTANON13,
    t.AUFUTANON14 = src.AUFUTANON14,
    t.AUFUTANON15 = src.AUFUTANON15,
    t.AUFUTANON16 = src.AUFUTANON16,
    t.AUMUSE = src.AUMUSE,
    t.AUPID = src.AUPID,
    t.AUJOBN = src.AUJOBN,
    t.AUUPMJ = src.AUUPMJ,
    t.AUUPMT = src.AUUPMT
WHEN NOT MATCHED THEN
  INSERT (AUUSER,
    AUWUID,
    AUROLEDESC,
    AULNGP,
    AUSEQNO,
    AUEMLA,
    AULASTLOGIN,
    AUUSEINTENSE,
    AUWEBIDCRE,
    AUACTINACT,
    AUFUTANON1,
    AUFUTANON2,
    AUFUTANON10,
    AUFUTANON11,
    AUFUTANON12,
    AUFUTANON3,
    AUFUTANON4,
    AUFUTANON5,
    AUFUTANON6,
    AUFUTANON7,
    AUFUTANON8,
    AUFUTANON9,
    AUFUTANON13,
    AUFUTANON14,
    AUFUTANON15,
    AUFUTANON16,
    AUMUSE,
    AUPID,
    AUJOBN,
    AUUPMJ,
    AUUPMT )
  VALUES (src.AUUSER, src.AUWUID, src.AUROLEDESC, src.AULNGP, src.AUSEQNO, src.AUEMLA, src.AULASTLOGIN, src.AUUSEINTENSE, src.AUWEBIDCRE, src.AUACTINACT, src.AUFUTANON1, src.AUFUTANON2, src.AUFUTANON10, src.AUFUTANON11, src.AUFUTANON12, src.AUFUTANON3, src.AUFUTANON4, src.AUFUTANON5, src.AUFUTANON6, src.AUFUTANON7, src.AUFUTANON8, src.AUFUTANON9, src.AUFUTANON13, src.AUFUTANON14, src.AUFUTANON15, src.AUFUTANON16, UPPER(src.AUMUSE), src.AUPID, src.AUJOBN, src.AUUPMJ, src.AUUPMT)

(

    FSUSER,
    FSOBNM,
    FSDTAI,
    FSFRDV,
    FSSY,
    FSOWDI,
    FSFMNM,
    FSFUNO,
    FSINSL,
    FSRUN,
    FSVWYN,
    FSA,
    FSCHNG,

)
VALUES (
    :FSSETY,
    :FSUSER,
    :FSOBNM,
    :FSDTAI,
    CASE WHEN :FSDTAI = 'MCU' THEN LPAD(:FSFRDV, 12, ' ') ELSE :FSFRDV END,

    :FSOWDI,
    :FSFMNM,
    :FSFUNO,
    :FSINSL,

    :FSCHNG,

    :FSADDC,
    :FSIOK,
    :FSICPY,
    :FSIUPT,
    :FSATN1,
    :FSATN2,
    :FSATN3,
    UPPER(:FSMUSE),
    :FSPID,
    :FSJOBN,
    :FSUPMJ,
    :FSUPMT,
    :FSEXITID,
    :FSTABID,

INSERT INTO #SCHEMA.SY#.F00950W
WITH base AS (
    SELECT
        (SYSTIMESTAMP AT TIME ZONE 'UTC'
         - TIMESTAMP '1970-01-01 00:00:00 UTC') AS diff
    FROM dual
)
SELECT
  SYS_CONTEXT('USERENV', 'IP_ADDRESS')
    || ':'
    || TRUNC(
           EXTRACT(DAY    FROM b.diff) * 86400000
         + EXTRACT(HOUR   FROM b.diff) * 3600000
         + EXTRACT(MINUTE FROM b.diff) * 60000
         + EXTRACT(SECOND FROM b.diff) * 1000
       )
    || ':' ||
    (ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY wswosety, wsobnm) - 1) AS WSOID,
  WSWOSETY,
  WSWOCAT,
  WSWOUSER,
  WSOBNM,
  WSFMNM,
  WSVER,
  WSWOBNM,
  WSSY,
  WSSYR,
  WSWOACTFLG,
  (CASE WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 0 THEN 'NONE' WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 1 THEN 'CREATE'  WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 2 THEN 'SHARE' WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 3 THEN 'MODIFY' ELSE ' ' END) WSWOSECLVL,
  WSWOVIEW,
  WSWODELTPU,
  WSWOUPDTPU,
  WSWOADDPU,
  WSWOADDPR,
  WSWOACCESS,
  WSWOSECOPT1,
  WSWOSECOPT2,
  WSWOSECOPT3,
  WSWOSECOPT4,
  WSWOVALUE1,
  WSWOVALUE2,
  WSWOUSERID,
  WSWOPRGID,
  WSWOMKEY,
  WSWOUTIME,
  WSWOTYP,
  WSWOSUBCAT,
  WSWOOBNMS,
  WSWOFUTID1,
  WSWOFUTID2,
  WSWOFU1,
  WSWOFU2,
  WSWOFU3,
  WSWOFU4,
  WSWOFU5,
  WSWOFU6,
  WSWOFU7,
  WSWOFU8,
  WSWOFU9,
  WSWOFU10
FROM (
SELECT 
  MAX(WSOID) WSOID,
  WSWOSETY WSWOSETY,
  WSWOCAT WSWOCAT,
  RLTOROLE WSWOUSER,
  WSOBNM WSOBNM, 
  WSFMNM WSFMNM,
  WSVER WSVER,
  WSWOBNM WSWOBNM,
  WSSY WSSY,
  WSSYR WSSYR,
  MAX(WSWOACTFLG) WSWOACTFLG,
  MAX(CASE WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 'NONE' THEN 0 WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 'CREATE' THEN 1 WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 'SHARE' THEN 2 WHEN WSWOSECLVL = 'MODIFY' THEN 3 END) WSWOSECLVL,
  MAX(WSWOVIEW) WSWOVIEW,
  MAX(WSWODELTPU) WSWODELTPU,
  MAX(WSWOUPDTPU) WSWOUPDTPU,
  MAX(WSWOADDPU) WSWOADDPU,
  MAX(WSWOADDPR) WSWOADDPR,
  MAX(WSWOACCESS) WSWOACCESS,
  MAX(WSWOSECOPT1) WSWOSECOPT1,
  MAX(WSWOSECOPT2) WSWOSECOPT2,
  MAX(WSWOSECOPT3) WSWOSECOPT3,
  MAX(WSWOSECOPT4) WSWOSECOPT4,
  MAX(WSWOVALUE1) WSWOVALUE1,
  MAX(WSWOVALUE2) WSWOVALUE2,
  MAX(WSWOUSERID) WSWOUSERID,
  MAX(WSWOPRGID) WSWOPRGID,
  MAX(WSWOMKEY) WSWOMKEY,
  MAX(WSWOUTIME) WSWOUTIME,
  MAX(WSWOTYP) WSWOTYP,
  MAX(WSWOSUBCAT) WSWOSUBCAT,
  MAX(WSWOOBNMS) WSWOOBNMS,
  MAX(WSWOFUTID1) WSWOFUTID1,
  MAX(WSWOFUTID2) WSWOFUTID2,
  MAX(WSWOFU1) WSWOFU1,
  MAX(WSWOFU2) WSWOFU2,
  MAX(WSWOFU3) WSWOFU3,
  MAX(WSWOFU4) WSWOFU4,
  MAX(WSWOFU5) WSWOFU5,
  MAX(WSWOFU6) WSWOFU6,
  MAX(WSWOFU7) WSWOFU7,
  MAX(WSWOFU8) WSWOFU8,
  MAX(WSWOFU9) WSWOFU9,
  MAX(WSWOFU10) WSWOFU10
FROM 
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F95921
INNER JOIN 
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F00950W F1
  ON WSWOUSER = RLFRROLE
WHERE 
  RLTOROLE = :RLTOROLE
  AND (RLEXPIRDATE = 0 OR RLEXPIRDATE > ((TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'YYYY') - 1900) * 1000 + TO_CHAR(SYSDATE, 'DDD')))
GROUP BY
  WSWOSETY,
  WSWOCAT,
  RLTOROLE,
  WSOBNM,
  WSFMNM,
  WSVER,
  WSWOBNM,
  WSSY,
  WSSYR
)
CROSS JOIN base b

SELECT 
  count(*) IS_FOUND
FROM
  #SCHEMA.SY#.F98OWSEC
WHERE
  SCUSER = :SCUSER
